      "updated": 1775186361163,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "At session start:\n\u2022 detect tool + repo + branch + cwd\n\u2022 retrieve canon slice + enduring memory + working memory\n\u2022 render clean prompt payload\n\nDuring session:\n\u2022 support remember / propose-canon actions\n\nAt session end:\n\u2022 summarize deltas\n\u2022 store working memory\n\u2022 send sacred proposals to reflection queue",
      "fontSize": 17,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "At session start:\n\u2022 detect tool + repo + branch + cwd\n\u2022 retrieve canon slice + enduring memory + working memory\n\u2022 render clean prompt payload\n\nDuring session:\n\u2022 support remember / propose-canon actions\n\nAt session end:\n\u2022 summarize deltas\n\u2022 store working memory\n\u2022 send sacred proposals to reflection queue",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 204
    },
