      "text": "CLI / harness: Rust or TypeScript\nIndex: SQLite + FTS5\nVault format: Markdown + YAML/JSON metadata\nTransport: local CLI + optional MCP server\nSecrets: OS keychain / age / sops / encrypted files\nReview UI: terminal UI or small local web app",
