      "text": "Reusable protocol across tools\n\nTools:\n\u2022 get_canon_slice()\n\u2022 search_memory()\n\u2022 propose_reflection()\n\u2022 promote_candidate()",
      "fontSize": 17,
      "fontFamily": 1,
